<note n="0194003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0194003">餘＝五【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0194004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0194004">唯＝惟【三】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0195001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0195001">合＝答【三】【宮】</note>
